               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430508-name-1576" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1576" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1576" type="surname" value="STEADMAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1576" type="given" value="JOHN TOFF"></interp>JOHN TOFF STEADMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Edward Elliott, and drive his van. On the 28th of April, I had a basket with a cloth in it, and some bread and meat, and cheese—I saw the prisoner and another come out of the Bald-faced Stag at Putney, as I was coming by—the prisoner came up to the near side of the van, and took the basket off a hook—I told him it was mine—he ran away, and threw it over the bridge—he was about twenty yards off when I overtook him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> You had other parcels of con<lb></lb>siderable value? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I had not known the prisoner before, nor the other man—I charged the other man, because he and the prisoner were toge<lb></lb>ther I thought—I saw the prisoner take the basket—I do not know whether he knew I saw him—I was feeding my horses when he took it off—he did</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184305080205"></xptr>
               <p>not run away—he stood and swore at me—I had been walking on the near side of my van, and the basket was on the near side.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">COURT</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How far had he got from the cart when you first noticed him with the basket? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About twenty yards—when he took it he put it under his arm—the other man did nothing—the bread and the meat could not be seen.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18430508-1704-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
